description: New Balance X OFFSPRING 20New Balance X Offspring is a pairing that dates back to early 2004, when the first of many exclusive packs launched. Looking back through the collections, the ‘Neal Street 60 ’ 577 is a model that stands out above the rest. Firstly, it was one of the more unique collaborations, in that it was actually a hybrid of two models, featuring a 577 upper on a 576 outsole. The colours were also iconic, with animal print overlays and stitch down embroidery, a first for New Balance at the time. Re-imagining this original concept and bringing it up to speed with the modern age, the first of the pack sees the 1500 Phantom Fit get the Neal Street treatment.Staying as true to the original as possible, the colours remain identical. product_name: Asics Gel - Lyte III, cream
description: The lifestyle division of the Japanese performance trainer brand ASICS, ASICS Tiger has come through with newness for the AW17 season including the Gel - Lyte III. This trainer is one of the most-loved ASICS Tiger shapes due to the refined, understated silhouette and iconic split-tongue. Features include nubuck uppers, suede overlays and underlays with tonal textures and a perforated toebox, sides and heel for extra breathability. The trainer is sat on a GEL-cushioned midsole and a rubber outsole with a Lycra collar and sockliner to finish this contemporary, clean trainer. Product Code: 108338

This trainer is one of the most-loved ASICS Tiger shapes due to the refined, understated silhouette and iconic split-tongue. Features include nubuck uppers, suede camo overlays and underlays with tonal textures and a perforated toebox, sides and heel for extra breathability. The trainer is sat on a GEL-cushioned midsole and a rubber outsole with a Lycra collar and sockliner to finish this contemporary, clean trainer. Product Code: 108552

Originally introduced as a basketball shoe, the trainer features modern updates via premium canvas uppers, a vulcanised sole, a tonal toe box and tonal laces. The shoe provides long lasting comfort with the improved cushioned footbed and is finished with nickel eyelets, Chuck Taylor branding to the heel and a contrasting apron stripe. Colour: Pink Product Code: 107921

product_name: New Balance X Norse Projects M 770 NP, brown
description: Once more New Balance and Norse Projects collaborate on a special project, this time celebrating the classic Made in England 770. Called the Lucem Hafnia by Norse Projects the colourway is inspired by the architecture of the University of Copenhagen's main building and the interior of the University library, established over 530 years ago. This new update includes embossed branding to the side wall, a smooth nubuck overlay, EVA midsole, rubber outsole, woven tongue label, two pairs of laces and is finished with Norse Projects branding on the insoles.  Colour: Brown Product Code: 107701
